Kako sušite kosu?
- Vetrom. - Vazduhom.

00:59:14.823 --> 00:59:18.660
A električni mikser za puter?
- Ne. Mutimo ga rukama.

00:59:18.744 --> 00:59:20.162
Prestanite! Umuknite!

00:59:27.669 --> 00:59:31.131
Kul seoce. Veoma amiško.

00:59:32.465 --> 00:59:35.801
Ejb, Zik, kako se zabavljate?

00:59:35.885 --> 00:59:39.139
Radimo.
- Stani malo. Stani.

00:59:40.014 --> 00:59:42.183
Kako se ti zabavljaš?

00:59:43.018 --> 00:59:44.437
Vidi ovo.

01:01:52.897 --> 01:01:53.898
Hvala.

01:01:56.775 --> 01:01:57.985
Hvala.

01:02:02.032 --> 01:02:03.242
Bože moj,

01:02:03.324 --> 01:02:08.371
